net.fathomsoft.nova.tree

Class MethodCallArgumentList

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.fathomsoft.nova.tree.Node
      • net.fathomsoft.nova.tree.ArgumentList
        • net.fathomsoft.nova.tree.MethodCallArgumentList

  • public class MethodCallArgumentList
extends ArgumentList
    Node extension that keeps track of all of the arguments that are passed during a method call. The children of this node are all Argument instances. They are stored in the order that they will be passed to the method call.
